parameters: $gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnOp.I didn’t expect to see her here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrWoOp>.Why the hell is she still here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiWoEx.She still has the soul inside of her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnOp.The soul? What are you talking about?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoOp.What has possessed her? You must tell me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.She has a demon’s soul inside of her.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoEx.I don’t know what happened to me. I remember Mother Superior speaking to me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx>.Mother Superior? She left the church with the other nuns.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaEx.The Mother Superior of Saint Dame University.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaEx.Yes! She came into the church while you were gone…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.I was frightened, but I do not remember much of what happened next.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx^.She’s a succubus. Her goal is sex.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe>.Are you telling me that she’s a demon?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe>.I know I’m a priest, but color me skeptical.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Diana does. You can’t hide it. I saw the files.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.And now you’re here to kill Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuWoCl.There is a demonic presence here. I’ve had visions of it.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaOp>.Whatever is here, it tried to brainwash Sister Judy.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuSaCl.It must be true. Father Parker… He was a monster.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaEx^.The priest you thought you knew was a demon named Daemalius.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.Madalyn was his sister and she took his soul…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaDe.That is how she’s able to move in and out of our world.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe>.She moves in and out of our world?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaDe.But why would she want Sister Judy?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaEx>.If what you say is true, we’re not exactly friendly with demonic spirits.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrWoOp>.My guess is as good as yours. But I’m not going to feel safe knowing a teleporting monster is roaming the woods.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaOp^.Diana… Do you think she’s looking for us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.What more can she want from us?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrBaDe>.Sounds like Sister Judy isn’t the only one that has a history with Madalyn.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.Because her husband was an Eclipse Guild leader…");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiFlOp.Congratulations, detective. Looks like you’ve figured it out.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrBaDe^.I don’t get it. Madalyn comes here to use Charles and then kill him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe^.What did she gain from him and why is she still here?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.I’m on the case. But it would help if you were honest with me.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnDe^.If you think we’re thieves, then why would we tell you anything?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnEx.You know why we’re here… We’re here for Duncan.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnEx^.You think the Guild is dying? It’s only changing leadership.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnDe.So Duncan is taking over where Charles left off?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.If Charles was a Guild leader, where are his subordinates? Where are the other Guild members?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiAnEx.The Guild is still operating here. And it’s not going away until Duncan Helmer is dead.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HrAnOp^.Come on, Diana. We don’t need his help.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "ChWoOp.Are they working on the same case as you, 1Hero?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McAnEx.They have connections to a criminal organization.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McSaDe.This case is complicated. It’s hard to explain.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "BrFrEx.Come on. Let’s get Sister Judy back inside.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "JuFrOp.Thank you for coming to my rescue. I am fortunate to have such caring people in my life.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.Of course, Judy. We couldn’t let anything bad happen to you.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McBaOp.This dead, dry tree could be chopped down if I had a hatchet.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McWoCl.Those bees look angry. I better keep my distance.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "McFrOp.I can use my blow torch to smoke out the bees.");
